  </intervention>
  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  · Dry eye disease diagnosis

               -  Patients must currently be using Systane tears at least once a day and for at
                  least 1 month.

               -  Normal lid position and closure

               -  Male or female of legal age of consent

               -  Informed consent has been obtained

               -  Likely to complete all required follow-up visits

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  · Concurrent enrollment in an investigational drug or device study, or participation
             in such a study within 30 days of entry into this study.

               -  Subject has a condition, or is in a situation which, in the investigator's
                  opinion, may put the subject at a significant risk, may confound the study
                  results, or may interfere significantly with the subject's participation in the
                  study.
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
    <gender>All</gender>
    <minimum_age>18 Years</minimum_age>
    <maximum_age>N/A</maximum_age>
  </eligibility>
